Proclamation under the Cooperatives Act 1999

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Cooperatives Act 1999 fix 24 May 2000 as the day on which that Act commences.

15 May 2000

G. S. M. GREEN

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

P. PATMORE

Minister for Justice and Industrial Relations

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 24 May 2000

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Justice and Industrial Relations.
